    {
      "id": "E:note:row681825:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "This is a 65 yo M with h/o MDS who is day +68 s/p nonablative matched    unrelat",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row681825#s1",
      "text": "This is a 65 yo M with h/o MDS who is day +68 s/p nonablative matched    unrelated donor stem cell transplant complicated by acute GVHD of the    skin and gut who initially presented with FTT and now is transferred to    the [**Hospital Unit Name 4**] in setting of worsening respiratory distress and hypoxia."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row681825:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Following his transplant on [**2126-4-11**], the patient has been nearly    cont",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row681825#s2",
      "text": "Following his transplant on [**2126-4-11**], the patient has been nearly    continuously hospitalized for complications of GVHD."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row681825:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "This current    admission has been complicated by worsening diarrhea [**2-4**] G",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row681825#s3",
      "text": "This current    admission has been complicated by worsening diarrhea [**2-4**] GVHD in    setting of attempts to wean down on steroids due to concern for a    possible occult infection as the patient was complaining of a cough and    weakness, intermittent AMS that was thought to be [**2-4**] delirium after    CT/MRI of the head were unrevealing."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row681825:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt had increased o2 requirements    [**6-18**] and was transferred to [**Wardnam",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row681825#s4",
      "text": "Pt had increased o2 requirements    [**6-18**] and was transferred to [**Wardname **] 4 ICU for further workup."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row681825:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Positive for    parainfluenza.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row681825#s5",
      "text": "Positive for    parainfluenza."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row681825:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Diarrhea    Assessment:    Pt with continuous liquid diarrhea, slowed around 010",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
